snippet.textDisplay: In a deep trance as I keep listening to Humera Arshad’s mesmerizing vocals! She has impeccable control over her powerful yet “sweet as honey” voice resulting in a flawless delivery. I hope it is not just a lone masterpiece as I expect Coke Studio to produce more ear-candy from this exceptionally talented voice. Humera’s vocal ability clearly puts her in the A-list of Pakistani singers. She has been underrated due to lack of quality productions such as this one by Coke Studio.
